title: Chrome Jun2016 ver (google) Portable installer (can keep on USB
description:
Chrome Jun2016 ver (google) Portable installer (can keep on USB drive) need web to download 150mb though

I came across this a few months ago. looked handy and could try out the
latest build without lossing the exist install windows one


the exe is a unpacker.. will unzip the files to location you want
a folder or USB drive

then just run the chromeportable.exe in the unzip folder

can install other things like plugins



can work with existing installed windows versions but I dont think they can run at the same time
